<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-18346] Error Unknown column during deserialization missing keyspace and table name</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18346</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ERROR message generated in ColumnSubselection.java when a column name is not found only prints the column name, not the keyspace and table.&#160; It can be difficult to track down the source when more than one table uses the same name.&#160; E.g., &apos;id&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;if (column == null)&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
{&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; column = metadata.getDroppedColumn(name);&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; if (column == null)&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; throw new UnknownColumnException(&quot;Unknown column &quot; + UTF8Type.instance.getString(name) + &quot; during deserialization&quot;);&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;}&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ERROR&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cluster_id=15 ip_address=192.168.65.10&#160; java.lang.RuntimeException: Unknown column id during deserialization&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Proposed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ERROR&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cluster_id=15 ip_address=192.168.65.10&#160; java.lang.RuntimeException: Unknown column id in table cycling.route during deserialization&lt;/p&gt;</description>
