                            <comment id="17720862" author="blerer" created="Tue, 9 May 2023 08:42:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The main reason for a Column to be missing is schema propagation. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17047&quot; title=&quot;Dropping a column can break queries until the schema is fully propagated (TAKE 2)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17047&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17047&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15899&quot; title=&quot;Dropping a column can break queries until the schema is fully propagated&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-15899&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-15899&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
